{"tid":2233301,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【中國又贏 全面加速】Pew Research民調：好多國家對中國嘅負皮達歷史新高","createTime":"2020-10-07T04:36:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T05:01:53.000Z","uid":138409,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2357ea02b14fa508e8d0828cbee9513545377a75","tid":2233301,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T04:36:04.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"xx-large\">全球反中</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.pewresearch.org/global/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/10/PG_2020.10.06_Global-Views-China_0-01.png?resize=640,821\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pewresearch.org%2Fglobal%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F2%2F2020%2F10%2FPG_2020.10.06_Global-Views-China_0-01.png%3Fresize%3D640%2C821&h=784861c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎：中國衰，美帝更衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.pewresearch.org/global/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/10/PG_2020.10.06_Global-Views-China_0-02.png?resize=640,426\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pewresearch.org%2Fglobal%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F2%2F2020%2F10%2FPG_2020.10.06_Global-Views-China_0-02.png%3Fresize%3D640%2C426&h=e4b8a03b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對習小學生 嘅負皮節節上升，又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.pewresearch.org/global/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/10/PG_2020.10.06_Global-Views-China_0-12.png?resize=640,717\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pewresearch.org%2Fglobal%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F2%2F2020%2F10%2FPG_2020.10.06_Global-Views-China_0-12.png%3Fresize%3D640%2C717&h=1c15aa07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"xx-large\">tl;dr</span></span>：<br />\n- 電話訪問總共14276人，來自14個國家<br />\n<br />\n- 大部分國家對中國評價負面，其中澳洲、英國、德國、荷蘭、瑞典、美國、南韓、西班牙、加拿大 對中國嘅負面評價，係自成個調查（十幾年前）開始以來<span class=\"gold\">歷史新高</span><br />\n<br />\n- <span class=\"gold\">對中國負皮升的最快嘅係澳洲</span>，比舊年升左24%，達81%；英國就升左19%，去到 74%；美國就升左13%去到 73%<br />\n<br />\n- <span class=\"gold\">負皮原因，來自中國對武漢肺炎嘅處理手法</span>；14個國家中，認為中國處理疫情得好差嘅受訪者比例，中位數係61%<br />\n<br />\n- 更重要係，對中國處理疫情嘅負皮，遠遠嚴重過受訪者對於自己國家 / 世衛 / 歐盟嘅負皮；<span class=\"gold\">不過對美國處理疫情嘅印象仲差</span><br />\n<br />\n- <span class=\"gold\">受訪者對習小學生 無信心嘅比例，中位數係78%；亦都係大部分國家嘅歷史新高，負皮比率往往亦都係比舊年double左</span><br />\n<br />\n- 但係大部分人都係對習小學生有信心過侵侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<blockquote>The survey also asked about confidence in five other world leaders. Only confidence in U.S. President Trump is lower than confidence in Xi. When considering median confidence, Russian President Vladimir Putin receives slightly higher marks, while confidence in European leaders Merkel, Macron and Johnson are at least twice as high as in Xi.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n- 基本上響所有國家，都係老人家對中負皮較多；<span class=\"gold\">唯獨係南韓，係年輕人對中國負皮較多</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n份報告值得仔細睇㗎<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pewresearch.org/global/2020/10/06/unfavorable-views-of-china-reach-historic-highs-in-many-countries/pg_2020-10-06_global-views-china_0-12/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pewresearch.org%2Fglobal%2F2020%2F10%2F06%2Funfavorable-views-of-china-reach-historic-highs-in-many-countries%2Fpg_2020-10-06_global-views-china_0-12%2F&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmV8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=a776b619\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pewresearch.org/global/2020/10/06/unfavorable-views-of-china-reach-historic-highs-in-many-countries/pg_2020-10-06_global-views-china_0-12/</a>"},{"pid":"63873307b78a51a7f697df0697607869e40c48bc","tid":2233301,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T04:36:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a5facc2d6ac54927830fae0dc3fc8be810789a5e","tid":2233301,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T04:36:47.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"849fc775ed02d2d2c1f44d7e672b4e5da3ceb54f","tid":2233301,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T04:37:15.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9b8b2de4eb798ee6b3643a5dc2bd0e6e0c17f91e","tid":2233301,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T04:37:35.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9ff0ba04ea62ae154f0a8f950f3026fe7e7d39cf","tid":2233301,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T04:38:20.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d4628cde60d588548022686bb0576eb9a6004064","tid":2233301,"uid":161684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T04:38:50.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"7be935c270ded44094dcb0bffb3e690edb5e00fa","tid":2233301,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T04:39:11.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"39cb2eb1436ad579f734fd9b9048ee1287f1830f","tid":2233301,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T04:39:34.000Z","msg":"btw<br />\n簽德國聯署啊啊啊啊<br />\n<br />\n德國政府官方聯署：夠數德國就必須喺國會討論制裁中國<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2229100\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2229100</a>"},{"pid":"165d473f22e462d1e27675ed4c69013779a74080","tid":2233301,"uid":62151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T04:40:05.000Z","msg":"民調係唔等於政府施政"},{"pid":"59280494a51b954aadae34bd436c22ed9bc8ffc4","tid":2233301,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T04:41:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"789a689550a186eb85cdffb6d1dcb499cf60f6b5","tid":2233301,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T04:42:06.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f0e296b02e0d42fcc3615d96adcdf51383f1dde8","tid":2233301,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T04:42:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"57a560ff36787f71275fa1c3d85